This is delicious and easy. I served a tart to my neighbors for breakfast and they raved about it. I used low-fat cream cheese, which tastes just as good as "full-fat". I'm not experienced at working with pastry sheets, so my tarts came out more square than the recipe calls for, but they looked and tasted great so don't worry if you can't exactly duplicate the pastry sizes and shapes the recipe has.

